node.text:
GRADUATION! My son Kennedy (@capitalfrenchies) has been through the ringer. But 3 spinal surgeries later, he has officially graduated from Physical Therapy. SO happy for him. Can you share some words of encouragement for Kennedy in the comments? I’ll share all the comments with him later 🐶 

P.S. Have you ever thought about Passive Income? My team and I are looking for a few more ppl who want to earn a full-time passive income from home using AirBNB without owning property. If you’re interested, message me the word "TRAVEL”. Thanks!

node.text: If you feel insecure about yourself, watch this.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jason Capital on September 18, 2021. May be an image of 3 people, people standing, sunglasses, outdoors and text that says 'OJAI IBELIEVE IN YOU EVEN IF YWDON'T'.

node.text:
WHY DO I wear shirts that say “I believe in you even if you don’t”? Because I do. I actually, genuinely do. Jung said that perception is projection. What you see outside of you comes from what’s going on inside of you. If I see you and believe you can do it, it has more to do with me than it does with you. And same you me. In this way, the world really is our mirror. How we’re perceiving what’s outside can be clues to what’s going on inside. And credit to my man Shen here, who looks like he could be modeling for an outdoor magazine in this pic. We were on a team retreat in Ojai, CA. 

P.S. Do you like Instagram? My team and I are looking for a few more ppl who want to earn a full-time income from home just typing messages on social media. If you’re interested, message me the word “MENTOR”. Thanks!
